    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity in &quot;The Rolling Room Demo&quot; the ultimate design and decorating game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo Features </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo includes 2 isometric rooms, a camper van, and a mini truck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around 200+ objects are available to decorate the rooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo features a save system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of the key features are mentioned below which are included in the demo version -</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Free Transform</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely scale, move, and rotate objects while viewing precise dimensions for perfect placement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/8bfd9d8a4c60031faec2c07c24502561.poster.avif?t=1767276202\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/8bfd9d8a4c60031faec2c07c24502561.webm?t=1767276202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/8bfd9d8a4c60031faec2c07c24502561.mp4?t=1767276202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Placement Freedom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break free from constraints. Place furniture anywhere without colliders and grids, allowing your creativity to flow effortlessly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/62258c924250d372ff165091dac60342.poster.avif?t=1767276202\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/62258c924250d372ff165091dac60342.webm?t=1767276202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/62258c924250d372ff165091dac60342.mp4?t=1767276202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate traditional rooms or take on the challenge of designing mobile spaces like camper vans and isometric rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/c7e6ceafb04e0bd97d7ee1618cde5428.poster.avif?t=1767276202\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/c7e6ceafb04e0bd97d7ee1618cde5428.webm?t=1767276202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225490/extras/c7e6ceafb04e0bd97d7ee1618cde5428.mp4?t=1767276202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raytracing support<br>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free camera movement<br>    <br>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Color swatches <br>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save color palette</p></li></ul>",
